</ul>
<p>All exercises and homeworks in this course will be done in jupyter notebooks. This <a href="https://www.dataquest.io/blog/jupyter-notebook-tutorial/">link</a> will help you setup jupyter lab and get you acquianted with jupyter notebooks.</p>
