<h2 id="parting-note">Parting Note</h2>
<p>As you will learn in the course, programming for data science is not just about writing efficient code.</p>
<p>It requires proficiency in critical thinking, ideation &amp; experimentation.</p>
<p>Keeping that in mind, you are advised to give your full active attention to every session.</p>
<p>We wish you well for the start of your data science journey.</p>
